Interface HasObjectiveCSources

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ObjectiveCApplication, ObjectiveCApplicationExtension, ObjectiveCIosApplication, ObjectiveCIosApplicationExtension, ObjectiveCLibrary, ObjectiveCLibraryExtension

    public interface HasObjectiveCSources
    Represents a component that carries Objective-C sources.

    • Method Detail

      • getObjectiveCSources

        default ObjectiveCSourceSet getObjectiveCSources()
        Defines the Objective-C sources of this component.

        By default, the source set contains all files in the directory src/componentName/objectiveC (and src/componentName/objc for backward compatibility), where componentName represent this component's name, i.e. main or test.

        Returns:
        a source set containing the Objective-C sources of this component, never null
        Since:
        0.5
        See Also:
        ObjectiveCSourceSet
